{
  "name": "finance",
  "version": "0.3.0",
  "kind": "blueprint",
  "module_directory": "finance",
  "description": "Finance blueprint covering Budgets + Paychecks + Invoices under spice/finance/. Top hub Finance.md aggregates pending items from all three sub-areas. Budgets/Paychecks are flat dated entities; Invoices use a per-month folder ecosystem mirroring trips/<slug>/. Status pills (Planning/In Progress/Done) derived from frontmatter via shared FinanceStatus helper. v0.2.7 PATCH: 8 outline-accent button call sites migrated to customJS.AccentButton.render. v0.2.8 PATCH (in-cycle CF-1): InvoiceControls Save now also recomputes amount = round(rate * hours, 2) on save; Save's enabled state additionally considers amount drift (enabled when stored amount != rate * hours) so stale-amount entities can be re-synced without changing the rate. Misleading caveat note removed. v0.3.0 MINOR (v0.46.0 S8+S9+S10): three New*Button classes (NewBudgetButton/NewPaycheckButton/NewInvoiceButton) deleted; manifest declares new_entity_buttons[] entries for budget/paycheck/invoice via entity-create@0.1.0 mechanism — schema extensions exercised: month/number prompt types, validate gte/min predicates, |number substitution pipe, inline_body, extra_files[] (invoice scaffolds Time-Log + Board sidecars). Total ~500 LOC of overlay-dialog code retired.",
  "depends_on": [
    { "name": "nav-buttons",    "range": ">=2.5.2" },
    { "name": "cards",          "range": ">=0.2.3" },
    { "name": "customjs-guard", "range": ">=1.0.0" },
    { "name": "accent-button",  "range": ">=0.1.0" },
    { "name": "convenience",    "range": ">=0.1.0" }
  ],
  "customjs_classes": [
    "FinanceStatus",
    "FinanceHubCards",
    "BudgetsCards",
    "PaychecksCards",
    "InvoicesCards",
    "InvoiceNavButtons",
    "FinanceFrontmatter",
    "BudgetNavButtons",
    "PaycheckNavButtons",
    "BudgetCategoriesEditor",
    "PaycheckExpensesEditor",
    "InvoiceTimeLogEditor",
    "InvoiceControls"
  ],
  "files": [
    { "source": "helpers/finance-status.js",       "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/finance-status.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/finance-hub-cards.js",    "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/finance-hub-cards.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/budgets-cards.js",        "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/budgets-cards.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/paychecks-cards.js",      "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/paychecks-cards.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/invoices-cards.js",       "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/invoices-cards.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/invoice-nav-buttons.js",  "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/invoice-nav-buttons.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/finance-frontmatter.js",       "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/finance-frontmatter.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/budget-nav-buttons.js",        "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/budget-nav-buttons.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/paycheck-nav-buttons.js",      "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/paycheck-nav-buttons.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/budget-categories-editor.js",  "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/budget-categories-editor.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/paycheck-expenses-editor.js",  "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/paycheck-expenses-editor.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/invoice-time-log-editor.js",   "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/invoice-time-log-editor.js" },
    { "source": "helpers/invoice-controls.js",          "dest": "{{scripts_path}}/finance/invoice-controls.js" },

    { "source": "content/Finance.md",              "dest": "{{module_directory}}/Finance.md" },
    { "source": "content/Budgets.md",              "dest": "{{module_directory}}/budgets/Budgets.md" },
    { "source": "content/Paychecks.md",            "dest": "{{module_directory}}/paychecks/Paychecks.md" },
    { "source": "content/Invoices.md",             "dest": "{{module_directory}}/invoices/Invoices.md" },

    { "source": "templates/Budget Template.md",         "dest": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Budget.md" },
    { "source": "templates/Paycheck Template.md",       "dest": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Paycheck.md" },
    { "source": "templates/Invoice Template.md",        "dest": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Invoice.md" },
    { "source": "templates/Time Log Template.md",       "dest": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Time Log.md" },
    { "source": "templates/Invoice Board.md",           "dest": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Invoice Board.md" },
    { "source": "templates/Invoice Board Card.md",      "dest": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Invoice Board Card.md" }
  ],
  "nav_buttons": [
    {
      "id": "finance-hub",
      "label": "Finance",
      "icon": "finance",
      "order": 120,
      "action": { "type": "openLink", "target": "{{module_directory}}/Finance.md" }
    }
  ],
  "templater_folder_templates": [
    { "folder": "{{module_directory}}/budgets",   "template": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Budget.md" },
    { "folder": "{{module_directory}}/paychecks", "template": "{{templates_path}}/Template, Paycheck.md" }
  ],
  "post_install": [
    {
      "type": "notice",
      "message": "Finance blueprint v0.1.0 installed at spice/finance/. Open spice/finance/Finance.md and click 'New Budget' / 'New Paycheck' / 'New Invoice' to scaffold entries. Status pills (Planning/In Progress/Done) derive from frontmatter at render time. Cmd+R required after this install to load 9 CustomJS classes."
    }
  ],
  "bootstrap_contributions": [
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.cc_active_cards",          "type": "string[]", "prompt": "Cards you actively spend from (comma-separated)",                "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] },
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.cc_locked_cards",          "type": "string[]", "prompt": "Cards you've frozen (comma-separated)",                          "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] },
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.cc_ignored_cards",         "type": "string[]", "prompt": "Cards you don't track (comma-separated)",                        "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] },
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.cc_focus_card",            "type": "string",   "prompt": "Highest-priority locked card name (single)",                     "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] },
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.debt_weekly_target_usd",   "type": "number",   "prompt": "Weekly debt-paydown target in USD (numeric)",                    "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] },
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.debt_monthly_target_usd",  "type": "number",   "prompt": "Monthly debt-paydown target in USD (numeric)",                   "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] },
    { "kind": "engagement_field_offer", "engagement_field_id": "finance.discretionary_categories", "type": "string[]", "prompt": "Discretionary spending categories (comma-separated)",            "consumed_by_types": ["personal"] },
    { "kind": "context_file_offer",     "path_template": "spice/cowork/context/{{engagement_id}}/finance-guide.md", "source_template": "engagement-templates/personal/finance-guide.md",            "consumed_by_types": ["personal", "consulting"] }
  ],
  "new_entity_buttons": [
    {
      "id": "budget",
      "label": "New Budget",
      "icon": "wallet-plus",
      "prompts": [
        { "key": "month", "label": "Month", "type": "month", "required": true, "default": "{{now.YYYY-MM}}" }
      ],
      "destination": {
        "folder_prefix": "spice/finance/budgets/{{prompts.month}}",
        "filename_prefix": "Budget-{{prompts.month}}"
      },
      "frontmatter_template": {
        "type": "budget",
        "budget_month": "{{prompts.month}}",
        "categories": [],
        "created": "{{now.YYYY-MM-DD}}",
        "tags": ["finance", "budget"],
        "cssclasses": ["wide"]
      },
      "inline_body": "```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"SpaceNavButtons\" });\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"BudgetNavButtons\" });\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait customJS.FinanceStatus.renderBadge(dv, \"budget\");\n```\n\n## Categories\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"BudgetCategoriesEditor\" });\n```\n",
      "render_in": { "kind": "hub", "target_path": "{{module_directory}}/budgets/Budgets.md" }
    },
    {
      "id": "paycheck",
      "label": "New Paycheck",
      "icon": "wallet-plus",
      "prompts": [
        { "key": "start_date", "label": "Start date", "type": "date", "required": true },
        { "key": "end_date",   "label": "End date",   "type": "date", "required": true, "validate": "gte:start_date" },
        { "key": "amount",     "label": "Amount",     "type": "number", "required": true, "min": 0 }
      ],
      "destination": {
        "folder_prefix": "spice/finance/paychecks/{{prompts.start_date}}",
        "filename_prefix": "Paycheck-{{prompts.start_date}}"
      },
      "frontmatter_template": {
        "type": "paycheck",
        "pay_period_start": "{{prompts.start_date}}",
        "pay_period_end": "{{prompts.end_date}}",
        "paycheck_amount": "{{prompts.amount|number}}",
        "expenses": [],
        "created": "{{now.YYYY-MM-DD}}",
        "tags": ["finance", "paycheck"],
        "cssclasses": ["wide"]
      },
      "inline_body": "```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"SpaceNavButtons\" });\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"PaycheckNavButtons\" });\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait customJS.FinanceStatus.renderBadge(dv, \"paycheck\");\n```\n\n## Expenses\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"PaycheckExpensesEditor\" });\n```\n",
      "render_in": { "kind": "hub", "target_path": "{{module_directory}}/paychecks/Paychecks.md" }
    },
    {
      "id": "invoice",
      "label": "New Invoice",
      "icon": "file-plus",
      "prompts": [
        { "key": "month", "label": "Month", "type": "month", "required": true, "default": "{{now.YYYY-MM}}" }
      ],
      "destination": {
        "folder_prefix": "spice/finance/invoices/{{prompts.month}}",
        "filename_prefix": "Invoice-{{prompts.month}}"
      },
      "frontmatter_template": {
        "type": "invoice",
        "month": "{{prompts.month}}",
        "date": "{{prompts.month}}-01",
        "rate": 0,
        "hours": 0,
        "amount": 0,
        "submitted_date": null,
        "created": "{{now.YYYY-MM-DD}}",
        "tags": ["finance", "invoice"],
        "cssclasses": ["wide"]
      },
      "inline_body": "```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"SpaceNavButtons\" });\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"InvoiceNavButtons\" });\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait customJS.FinanceStatus.renderBadge(dv, \"invoice\");\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"InvoiceControls\" });\n```\n",
      "extra_files": [
        {
          "filename_pattern": "Time-Log-{{prompts.month}}.md",
          "frontmatter_template": {
            "type": "time-log",
            "month": "{{prompts.month}}",
            "date": "{{prompts.month}}-01",
            "total_hours": 0,
            "entries": [],
            "created": "{{now.YYYY-MM-DD}}",
            "tags": ["finance", "time-log"],
            "cssclasses": ["wide"]
          },
          "inline_body": "%% nav buttons rendered conditionally — suppressed when this note is embedded elsewhere %%\n```dataviewjs\nconst isEmbedded = dv.container.closest(\".markdown-embed\") != null;\nif (!isEmbedded) {\n    await dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"SpaceNavButtons\" });\n    await dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"InvoiceNavButtons\" });\n}\n```\n\n```dataviewjs\nawait dv.view(\"ranch/views/customjs-guard\", { class: \"InvoiceTimeLogEditor\" });\n```\n"
        },
        {
          "filename_pattern": "Board-{{prompts.month}}.md",
          "subfolder": "board",
          "frontmatter_template": {
            "kanban-plugin": "board",
            "title": "Invoice {{prompts.month}} Board",
            "type": "kanban",
            "tags": ["board", "finance", "invoice/{{prompts.month}}"]
          },
          "inline_body": "## To Do\n\n## In Progress\n\n## Completed\n\n%% kanban:settings\n```\n{\"kanban-plugin\":\"board\",\"list-collapse\":[false,false,false],\"new-note-folder\":\"spice/finance/invoices/{{prompts.month}}/board\",\"new-note-template\":\"ranch/templates/Template, Invoice Board Card.md\"}\n```\n%%\n"
        }
      ],
      "render_in": { "kind": "hub", "target_path": "{{module_directory}}/invoices/Invoices.md" }
    }
  ],
  "rule_fragments": []
}
